<body role="main">
  <%= debug @opportunity%>
    <section id="intro">
      <div class="left_side">
        <h2>Hello &amp; Welcome</h2>
        <p>Have you ever had the thought of helping others but didn't know where to start? Helping hand is your answer. We are a web based application pairing those in need with those who are wishing to help. For those wanting to find where in their area they may be of need, our application provides a list of current opportunities and the amount of individuals needed.</p>
        <div class="flexslider">
          <ul class="slides">
            <li>
              <%= image_tag("food_web.jpg") %>
              <p class="flex-caption">Captions and cupcakes. Winning combination.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
              <%= image_tag("food_web.jpg") %>
            </li>
            <li>
              <%= image_tag("food_web.jpg") %>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <ul>
          <%= @opportunity.each do |bob| %>
            <h1><%= bob.name %></h1>
            <p><%= bob.description %></p>
            <ul>
              <li><%= bob.location%></li>
              <li><%= bob.event_start%></li>
              <li><%= bob.event_end%></li>
            </ul>
          <% end %>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="right_side">
        <div id="search_area">
          <h2>Find an opportunity</h2>
          <form class="navbar-search pull-left">
            <input type="text" class="search-query" placeholder="Search">
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div id="view_list">
      </div>
    </section>
</body>
